            <title>[HBASE-14111] Enable HBase ACL in REST operations</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-14111</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently for any operations performed by users through REST service, the internal HBase ACL is bypassed and users can perform any operation without security restrictions (they can view and insert data to any location).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
